<h6 class="kicker"><a href="//dealbook.blogs.nytimes.com/category/hedge-funds/">HEDGE FUNDS &#187;</a></h6>
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Soros Collects $5.5 Billion on Quantum Endowmentâs Success <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> Quantum Endowment, George Sorosâs hedge fund, had its second-best year in dollar terms last year, netting Mr. Soros $5.5 billion and returning Quantum to the top place among the most successful hedge funds ever, The Financial Times reports.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/296e38da-902b-11e3-8029-00144feab7de.html?siteedition=intl#axzz2srjK5vXp"> FINANCIAL TIMES </a></span></p>
